<figureCitation box="[101,180,986,1011]" captionStart="Figures 43-48" captionStartId="10.[869,937,2010,2035]" captionTargetBox="[873,1490,1055,1976]" captionTargetId="figure-666@10.[869,1493,1054,1980]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="Figures 43-48: Coxites of Macromalthinus species. (43) M. guyanensis sp. nov. (44) M. luteoapicalis sp. nov. (45) M. orapuensis sp. nov. (46) M. piceiventris sp. nov. (47) M. quadratithorax sp. nov. (48) M. xerophilus sp. nov. Scale bars:0.2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5384164" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5384164/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Fig. 44</figureCitation>
